  "texts": [
    "c, Uninformative visualization.",
    "A single box plot (left) does not give sufficient information about the raw metric value distribution.",
    "Adding the raw metric values as jittered dots on top (right) adds important information (here, on clusters).",
    "In the case of non-independent validation data, color-or shape-coding helps reveal data clusters.",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s41592-023-02150-0 of identified pitfalls, our taxonomy crucially establishes structure in the topic."
